oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Rock N' Roll Reunion at the Sutler
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Fairlanes (Musical group : Alabama); Monarchs (Musical group : Kentucky); Kingsmen (Gospel group); Woodcuts (prints);
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: One color window card (blue on pink) announcing Rock N' Roll Reunion featuring members of the Fairlanes, the Capers, the Deltas, the Sliders, the Monarchs, the Showmen, the Kingsmen, and Bruce Chanel at the Sutler on May 18. Poster features a woodcut of a horse and rider.
